is\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.199223451350011e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop, whose real name is Calvin Broadus Jr, gave US athlete and tennis star Coco Gauff one of these pins in an exchange documented on Instagram.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Calvin Broadus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}, {\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8951936240285177e-34, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A video in collaboration with the United States Tennis Association, Team USA, Snoop Dogg and the Women's Tennis Association showed the rapper wearing a T-shirt with Coco on it.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"United States Tennis Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Tennis_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1022, \"end\": 103